subject: Further to the previous commun
body:
Further to the previous communications Dr. Angelina De Dios had with you
in respect of your $7.6m that have been in our bank vault ever since.
Just to let you know that your funds ($7.6m) are already in the US this
moment. This action became quite imperative in order to prevent your
funds final evacuation to the Swiss Apex bank within this week. I had
to promptly package them into our bank normal official delivery trunk
box and smuggled it into the same official delivery inventory for two
other clients deliveries in the States. The three trunk boxes are
presently kept in a storage facility in the States. Yours is clearly
marked in your name. The trunk boxes were delivered recently
through a logistic charter on behalf of three of you. One of the
trunk box is for a client in Florida while the other trunk box belongs to
another client in New Jersey. Whilst your own trunk box is also routed for
delivery directly to you. I felt compelled at this juncture to safeguard your
funds especially like a woman even though you have always
discouraged me from communicating with you.
So, I will be able to furnish you with the official contact details of
the Logistics officer that accompanied the boxes for you to process
the seamless official delivery of your trunk box to you as soon as
possible.
Meanwhile, in case you eventually did not take delivery of your trunk
box, I will then officially redirect the delivery to forestall any untoward
issues in respect of the funds as a safeguard measure..
I now await your communication soonest.
Sincere Regards.
Dr. Alicia Burns
Principal Manager, Funds Control and Deliveries,
UBS AG,

subject: Re: Further to the previous commun
body:
Hello Dr. Alicia Burns,

Thank you for reaching out to me regarding my funds. I appreciate your efforts in ensuring the safekeeping of my money. Could you please provide me with more details about the logistics officer who will be handling the delivery of my trunk box? I would like to know their name and contact information so that I can get in touch with them directly.

Also, could you clarify what you mean by redirecting the delivery if I don't take immediate possession of the trunk box? What would be the process for redirecting it and how can we ensure that there won't be any issues with the funds?

I look forward to your prompt response.

Best wishes,
Juan
